1. Baskı
I Have a Story  Treasures of Anatolia
https://imageserver.kitapyurdu.com/select.php?imageid=5968581&width=500&isWatermarked=true
2018-05-14
 11,28
Anatolia is a land where history pullulates from every corner and where a rich culture winds the daily life.The amazing aspects of cultural heritage that have been preserved for thousands of years and reaching daily are in this book.When we say Anatolian cultural heritage, we do not talk about İstanbul, Antalya or Cappadocia; or about sea, sand and son are not our topic. Baklava, kebab or Turkish delight is also not.We wanted to bring light on interesting events, surprising stories and our values which are not known probably even by people living in Turkey.We presented a photo of completely different Turkey with delightful studies.We designed a unique Anatolian journey on the pages of this delicious book.Are you ready for a colorful journey in the history which is adorned with amazing stories? 
